Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.Entity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Entity>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReflectiveEntity

    public class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Entity>
    The Entity class is the base for all renderable objects along with non-renderable ones.
    Author:
    Ethan Vrhel
